<ns2904:section xmlns:ns2904="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.concepts.architecture.mda.introduction.coreFeatures">

  <ns2905:title xmlns:ns2905="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Core features of the MDA</ns2905:title>
  <ns2906:para xmlns:ns2906="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    The MDA specification is a compact specification. It's core features include
    <ns2907:itemizedlist xmlns:ns2907="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      <ns2908:listitem xmlns:ns2908="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns2909:para xmlns:ns2909="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        the generation of a <ns2910:emphasis xmlns:ns2910="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">platform-independent model</ns2910:emphasis> (PIM),
      </ns2909:para></ns2908:listitem>
      <ns2911:listitem xmlns:ns2911="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns2912:para xmlns:ns2912="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        <ns2913:emphasis xmlns:ns2913="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">standard mappings</ns2913:emphasis> onto common implementation technologies, 
      </ns2912:para></ns2911:listitem>
      <ns2914:listitem xmlns:ns2914="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns2915:para xmlns:ns2915="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        the generation of a <ns2916:emphasis xmlns:ns2916="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">platform-specific model</ns2916:emphasis> (PSM) from the
        platform independent model via the standard mappings, and
      </ns2915:para></ns2914:listitem>
      <ns2917:listitem xmlns:ns2917="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns2918:para xmlns:ns2918="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        ultimately the generation of the <ns2919:emphasis xmlns:ns2919="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Enterprise Deployment Model</ns2919:emphasis> (EDM) 
        from the platform specific model (PSM).  The EDM is the code for a specific platform.
      </ns2918:para></ns2917:listitem>
    </ns2907:itemizedlist>
    
  </ns2906:para>
</ns2904:section>